modules.description: This module provides direct conversions between URI types and S-expressions, enabling serialization and deserialization of `Uri.t` and `Uri.component` values. It includes functions to convert S-expressions to URI components and full URIs, as well as comparison and equality checks for URIs. Concrete use cases include persisting URIs to disk in S-expression format and transmitting URI values across systems that use S-expressions for data exchange.
